text: Dance Into Happiness () is a 1930 German musical movie directed by Max Nosseck (who also stars) and also starring Ilse Stobrawa, Fred Doederlein, Lotte Hané, Alwin Neuß, Heinrich Gotho. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 musical movies Category:German musical movies Category:Movies directed by Max Nosseck
title: Dance Into Happiness
